snippet.title: Hippo: Little Red Riding Hood - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Get now: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/hippo-little-red-riding-hood-switch/

Funny storie for children about the fascinating adventures of the Hippo. Visit the magical world of Little Red Riding Hood with Hippo and save her Grandma from an angry Dragon. Fun tasks and colorful puzzles with coloring for kids are waiting for you! Coming soon to Nintendo Switch!
